  "slug": "mob-spawning-light-level",
  "title": "Mob Spawning Light Level",
  "description": "Control the light level mobs spawn at with /gamerule mobSpawningLightLevel",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"text-decoration: underline; color: #000000; font-size: 24px; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong>Control the light level that mobs spawn!</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #800080; font-size: 24px; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong>/gamerule mobSpawningLightLevel</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 12px; color: #ff0000; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong><em>Only needs to be installed on the server!</em></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/fabric-api\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ol1Tcf8.png\" width=\"200\" height=\"67\" /></strong></span></a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">This mod adds <strong>/gamerule mobSpawningLightLevel</strong> that allows changing the light level at which hostile mobs can spawn. This allows mobs to spawn only in complete darkness or in a completely lit area!</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/635dfcf60b021359eabec53a28263754.png\" width=\"900\" /><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #333333;\"><em>Mobs can only spawn at light level 0</em></span></strong></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/f0f16563f1557fb892dd058daac56437.png\" width=\"900\" height=\"314\" /><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #333333;\"><em>Mobs can spawn at light level 7 and below (same as normal)</em></span></strong></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/5dd1c46f20b256c73cfdabea59f2748e.png\" width=\"900\" height=\"314\" /><span style=\"font-size: 18px; color: #333333;\"><em>Mobs can spawn at light level 10 and below</em></span></strong></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.gyazo.com/43531f82d36e7130aa5d74783f455a6d.png\" width=\"900\" height=\"314\" /><span style=\"color: #333333; font-size: 18px;\"><em>Mobs can spawn at any light level</em></span></strong></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><span style=\"color: #333333; font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"color: #333333; font-size: 18px;\"><em><a href=\"https://www.patreon.com/furgl_and_2piradians\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/g2vJewK.png\" alt=\"Patreon\" width=\"300\" height=\"70\" /></a><a href=\"https://discord.gg/kr8J5Zk3HR\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/cbfIsqM.png\" alt=\"Discord\" width=\"219\" height=\"70\" /></a></em></span></strong></span></span></p>",
